        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to my Portfolio</h1>
            <p>Within you will find many things about me and my skills</p>
            <a href="#about" class="pure-button menu-trigger" data-section="about">Learn More</a>
        </header>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="panel menu-section">
        <header><h2>About Me</h2></header>
        <p>
            I am a self taught software engineer with over 15 years of extensive experience in primarily web
            development. Through the years I have been able to branch out some and get experience with desktop
            applications as well. I have also, through my own curiousness, built back end services as well like
            an IRC bot.
        </p>
